com.orgsync.api

Interface EventsResource


  • public interface EventsResource

    Access to the events resource from the OrgSync API. This allows a client to query the events and get a list of events for a given org.

    See: https://api.orgsync.com/api/docs/v2/events

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ListenableFuture<ApiResponse<List<Event>>> getEvents(EventQueryParams params)
      Get A list of events based on the given EventQueryParams.
      ListenableFuture<ApiResponse<List<Event>>> getOrgEvents(int orgId, EventQueryParams params)
      Get the events for a given org and query params.

    • Method Detail

      • getEvents

        ListenableFuture<ApiResponse<List<Event>>> getEvents(EventQueryParams params)
        Get A list of events based on the given EventQueryParams. To get all events, pass a new EventQueryParams with no fields set.
        Parameters:
        params - the params to search by
        Returns:
        a future to the response of a list of events

      • getOrgEvents

        ListenableFuture<ApiResponse<List<Event>>> getOrgEvents(int orgId,
                                                      EventQueryParams params)
        Get the events for a given org and query params. TO get all events, use a new EventQueryParams with no fields set.
        Parameters:
        orgId - the org to get events for
        params - the params to search by
        Returns:
        a future to the response of a list of events
